63
00:05:10.490 --> 00:05:12.290
Krim kulit.

64
00:05:16.490 --> 00:05:17.451
Tanxiang.

65
00:05:18.184 --> 00:05:21.091
Barang bagus ini untukmu saja.

66
00:05:21.879 --> 00:05:23.050
Nona.

67
